article.description: Amari McCray scored 19 points off the bench to lead Pacific to a 60-53 win over Loyola Marymount on Thursday night.
article.headline: McCray's 19 points lead Pacific past Loyola Marymount 60-53
article.linkText: McCray's 19 points lead Pacific past Loyola Marymount 60-53
article.story: LOS ANGELES, Calif. -- Amari McCray scored 19 points off the bench to lead Pacific to a 60-53 win over Loyola Marymount on Thursday night. Jahlil Tripp and Broc Finstuen added 10 points apiece for Pacific (22-9, 10-5 West Coast Conference), while Seikou Sisoho Jawara paced Loyola Marymount (10-19, 4-11) with 12 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25
